OL,5, A toddler with a rare inherited        
OL,6, condition has become the first child to
OL,7, be treated by the NHS with a new       
OL,8, life-saving gene therapy.              
OL,10,FTeddi Shaw was diagnosed in time       
OL,11,Fbecause her older sister Nala showed   
OL,12,Fsymptoms - but it was too late to treat
OL,13,FNala, who is now terminally ill.       
OL,15,FBoth girls have MLD, which severely    
OL,16,Fdamages the brain and nervous system.  
OL,18,FThe one-off treatment costs #2.875m and
OL,19,Fis the most expensive medicine ever    
OL,20,Fapproved for the NHS.                  
